{"thag10.3:0.1":"Theragatha 10.3 ","thag10.3:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","thag10.3:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag10.3:0.4":"Mahakappinattheragatha ","thag10.3:1.1":"“Anagatam yo patikacca passati, ","thag10.3:1.2":"Hitanca attham ahitanca tam dvayam; ","thag10.3:1.3":"Viddesino tassa hitesino va, ","thag10.3:1.4":"Randham na passanti samekkhamana. ","thag10.3:2.1":"Anapanasati yassa, ","thag10.3:2.2":"paripunna subhavita; ","thag10.3:2.3":"Anupubbam paricita, ","thag10.3:2.4":"yatha buddhena desita; ","thag10.3:2.5":"Somam lokam pabhaseti, ","thag10.3:2.6":"abbha muttova candima. ","thag10.3:3.1":"Odatam vata me cittam, ","thag10.3:3.2":"appamanam subhavitam; ","thag10.3:3.3":"Nibbiddham paggahitanca, ","thag10.3:3.4":"sabba obhasate disa. ","thag10.3:4.1":"Jivate vapi sappanno, ","thag10.3:4.2":"api vittaparikkhayo; ","thag10.3:4.3":"Pannaya ca alabhena, ","thag10.3:4.4":"vittavapi na jivati. ","thag10.3:5.1":"Panna sutavinicchini, ","thag10.3:5.2":"Panna kittisilokavaddhani; ","thag10.3:5.3":"Pannasahito naro idha, ","thag10.3:5.4":"Api dukkhesu sukhani vindati. ","thag10.3:6.1":"Nayam ajjatano dhammo, ","thag10.3:6.2":"nacchero napi abbhuto; ","thag10.3:6.3":"Yattha jayetha miyetha, ","thag10.3:6.4":"tattha kim viya abbhutam. ","thag10.3:7.1":"Anantaram hi jatassa, ","thag10.3:7.2":"jivita maranam dhuvam; ","thag10.3:7.3":"Jata jata marantidha, ","thag10.3:7.4":"evamdhamma hi panino. ","thag10.3:8.1":"Na hetadatthaya matassa hoti, ","thag10.3:8.2":"Yam jivitattham paraporisanam; ","thag10.3:8.3":"Matamhi runnam na yaso na lokyam, ","thag10.3:8.4":"Na vannitam samanabrahmanehi. ","thag10.3:9.1":"Cakkhum sariram upahanti tena, ","thag10.3:9.2":"Nihiyati vannabalam mati ca; ","thag10.3:9.3":"Anandino tassa disa bhavanti, ","thag10.3:9.4":"Hitesino nassa sukhi bhavanti. ","thag10.3:10.1":"Tasma hi iccheyya kule vasante, ","thag10.3:10.2":"Medhavino ceva bahussute ca; ","thag10.3:10.3":"Yesam hi pannavibhavena kiccam, ","thag10.3:10.4":"Taranti navaya nadimva punnan”ti. ","thag10.3:10.5":"… Mahakappino thero …. "}